    "body": "I did a bit of testing. It doesn't work when applied using inline styles but it should work if you use a css rule instead. For example:\n\n``` css\nbody {\n  -webkit-app-region: drag;\n}\n```\n\nThis is possibly still a bug though (albeit title is incorrect) because I guess inline styles should also work.\n\nedit: It seems that inline styles do work but they don't seem to work when changed dynamically (e.g. via the devtools).\n"
