    "updated_at": "2016-10-02T11:36:44Z",
    "body": "All this works correctly for for me. The only thing that doesn't work is when the inline `-webkit-app-region` style is changed dynamically.\n\nYour issues are possibly something to do with the fact that your element with content (`<header />`) doesn't have layout properties because it is absolutely positioned. It would be easier to test if you put this in a repo rather than a gist.\n"
